{"tid":2338223,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國國防參謀長卡特：我們需為必要戰爭做好準備 劍指中國","createTime":"2020-12-24T01:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T15:13:48.000Z","uid":53844,"like":53,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"91bf3ed93864bd7a941e470e027ea5f860ab9b53","tid":2338223,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:24:45.000Z","msg":"英國國防參謀長卡特（Nick Carter）17日在英國皇家聯合研究所 （RUSI）演說提到，英軍的當務之急是為下一場必要戰爭作好準備，他將中國定義為「長期挑戰」，並認為最理想的策略是「以子之矛，攻子之盾」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，卡特在英國皇家聯合研究所指出，去年於相同時間、場合發言時，沒人預料到武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）大流行，這場疫情讓許多問題更加突出，「我們面臨2個特別重要的抉擇，第1個是選擇要遵從極權主義或公民賦權的社會；第2個是要選擇民族主義孤立或與全球團結」。<br />\n<br />\n卡特表示，疫情增加全球對抗、競爭與衝突，對英國而言，國安、價值觀與繁榮都受到影響，而中國透過數字基礎建設，將許多不富裕的國家吸引到其勢力範圍內，「他們的目標是不戰而屈人之兵，破壞我們的意志力，或運用其他攻擊來達到目的，而這些舉動會引發戰爭。」<br />\n<br />\n卡特強調，「我們正處於一個巨大變化的時期」，「如果有必要，而且可能的話，我們必須說服我們的潛在對手，這種『比賽』是不值得的」，卡特也提到，我們的當務之急是進行武裝、訓練和讓軍備就緒，為下一場必要戰爭作好準備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3387970?fbclid=IwAR25xNY-NZnl4RpNu8bXX2qZvcCu7L80VJiOhT9iZrqggsvZ40xcNOnRfco\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3387970%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR25xNY-NZnl4RpNu8bXX2qZvcCu7L80VJiOhT9iZrqggsvZ40xcNOnRfco&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=5be20132\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3387970%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR25xNY-NZnl4RpNu8bXX2qZvcCu7L80VJiOhT9iZrqggsvZ40xcNOnRfco&h=9cf3ddc3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3387970?fbclid=IwAR25xNY-NZnl4RpNu8bXX2qZvcCu7L80VJiOhT9iZrqggsvZ40xcNOnRfco</a>"},{"pid":"4cb965b7d6f993f612f17a16e23dc9c75f4fd926","tid":2338223,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abed2b9d5183ede47a3876d89d47760dede0b98","tid":2338223,"uid":33874,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:27:55.000Z","msg":"以子之矛英文係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時係咪會推班BNO出去做馬前卒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c7ee5ff9681617b63b8dc994c1e1ea021090dc","tid":2338223,"uid":11454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:30:46.000Z","msg":"仲長期挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生化戰打到就被人滅國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d761670dca9416ba3030730fbe4ab446fad9ed","tid":2338223,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:30:48.000Z","msg":"英文原文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/speeches/chief-of-defence-staff-at-rusi-annual-lecture\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fspeeches%2Fchief-of-defence-staff-at-rusi-annual-lecture&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=423a0643\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/speeches/chief-of-defence-staff-at-rusi-annual-lecture</a>"},{"pid":"e7fe1d5c168f10fdac9c0747a5762bdbb1fc8add","tid":2338223,"uid":228793,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:32:13.000Z","msg":"卡特中文唔錯...不戰而屈人之兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c694208779c58f4129557cd3d7bdcbdff4b2e4","tid":2338223,"uid":123189,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:36:34.000Z","msg":"咪姐係唔出兵囉<br />\n講咁多廢話駁曝光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4978f571319d38cddcb1742bb01e27d3e972b5","tid":2338223,"uid":60434,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:37:01.000Z","msg":"一隻毒都收你皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7ec389206ee9a46c7af51e288b69088f09fcf0","tid":2338223,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12